review_title: I ended up at Salma's instead
review_text: Tried to visit yesterday afternoon for drinks with a friend. This bar is on a close with a narrow road and there were cars parked all the way down. There was one spot which 'security' blocked off directing us to find where to park by...ourselves. So we went to Salma's. Because I can't be begging people to take my money.More
very okay they have the best disk jockey in lagos island for both new school and old school music . good security and nice pool
